      "name": "Invisible Armor",
      "description": "Aamon enters the Camouflage state each time he hits an enemy with a skill, during which he cannot be targeted, recovers 25 (+15% Total Magic Power) plus 3% of his lost HP every 0.5s, and gains 80% extra Movement Speed that rapidly decays over 3s.\nUpon leaving the Camouflage state, Aamon immediately resets his Basic Attack's cooldown and enhances his Basic Attacks within the next 3s. Each enhanced Basic Attack deals 70 (+100% Total Physical Attack) (+115% Total Magic Power) Magic Damage. The first attack after actively leaving Camouflage is enhanced to deal 84 (120% Physical Attack) (+138% Total Magic Power) damage and reduces all skill cooldowns by 1s.\n|quote=For generations, the Invisible Armor has been used as the symbol of the greatest power in House Paxley.",
